'''Pirate Squadron''' was a [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wing]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] that was operated by a pirate group based somewhere in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]]. Shortly before the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], Pirate Squadron and [[Toscan 8-Q starfighter|Toscan 8-Q]] squadron [[Fury Squadron|Fury]] accompanied [[Marauder-class Assault Corvette/Legends|Marauder Corvette]] ''[[Vulture (Marauder-class)|Vulture]]'' on a raid against casino owner [[Dunari]]. Unfortunately, Dunari was defended by [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunters]] of [[Bandit Squadron]] from the [[Mon Calamari Star Cruiser/Legends|Mon Calamari Star Cruiser]] [[Liberty/Legends|''Liberty'']], who fought off the pirates and inflicted heavy losses.

